<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> rājarāja</hi> tevaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="16"><g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num><g type="dash"/>vatu nāyanār tirukkāḷattiuṭai
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ya nāyaṉārkku kiḻaippaṭṭaiyanāṭṭuc ciṟṟeṭṭiṟ veḷḷāḷaril vaṭukami
<lb n="3" break="no"/>raṭṭi makaṉ vaṭukamiraṭṭi tirununtāviḷakku 1- kku viṭṭa Āṭu <num value="96">9 <g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num> poliki
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭāy 2 polimottai 2 Ivvāṭu toṇṇūṟṟāṟum polikiṭāy Iraṇ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭum polimottai Iraṇṭum Ikkoyiṟ tiruviḷak kiṭaiyaril cāṇak
<lb n="6" break="no"/>koṉ malaiyāḻvān viḷakku va kaṅkaṉ viḷakku va va<supplied reason="omitted">ṅ</supplied>kakkoṉ makaṉ ci
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṅka<unclear>ṉa</unclear>racaṉum<note n="247-1">Two more letters vaṉu are engraved below the line at this place.</note>viḷakku I Āka viḷakku Oṉṟu <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
